g_npc_450_1#9$1","id":15},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极境","text":"我可算求求你了，下次再有这种事情能不能提前打个招呼？再演下去，我可就救不了你了！","id":16,"figure":["avg_npc_450_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1","id":17},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"......哼。","id":18,"figure":["avg_npc_451_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"情况怎么样了？那个女人的怪物，把他们烧光了吗？","id":20,"figure":["avg_npc_451_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_450_1#9$1","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极境","text":"我不清楚，大概吧，Mon3tr火力全开的样子我也只在作战录像里看过啊......","id":22,"figure":["avg_npc_450_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#7$1","id":23},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"......烧吧。烧吧。","id":24,"figure":["avg_npc_451_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#7$1","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"格兰法洛已经是过去的事情了......全烧了吧。","id":26,"figure":["avg_npc_451_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_450_1#2$1","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极境","text":"......蒂亚戈先生。你......","id":28,"figure":["avg_npc_450_1",1]},{"type":"dialog","id":29},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":30},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.1","blackend":"0.25","fadetime":"1","id":31},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":32},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":33},{"type":"dialogue","name":"烧伤的教徒","text":"......哦，叛徒！还有伊比利亚人！我嗅到了你们的味道，你们在这里！","id":34,"figure":["avg_npc_453_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"烧伤的教徒","text":"你们来得正好。你们来得正好——！","id":35,"figure":["avg_npc_453_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_450_1#5$1","id":36},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极境","text":"——你是怎么？！","id":37,"figure":["avg_npc_450_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#4$1","id":38},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"哼，他已经瞎了，面目全非，那只怪物让他好受，活该！","id":39,"figure":["avg_npc_451_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#4$1","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"活该！听见了吗？！","id":41,"figure":["avg_npc_451_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.1","blackend":"0.25","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"烧伤的教徒","text":"活该？啊，是啊，蒂亚戈，我竟然选择信任一个被仇恨驱使的人，我竟然还对你这样的人抱有幻想，我确实活该。","id":43,"figure":["avg_npc_453_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"烧伤的教徒","text":"但现在，不同，了。（骨骼摩擦的声音）","id":44,"figure":["avg_npc_453_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":45},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":46},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_fish_howl","id":47},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_457_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_457_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":48},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":49},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_450_1#12$1","id":50},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极境","text":"——恐鱼？什么时候？","id":51,"figure":["avg_npc_450_1",11]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_450_1#12$1","id":52},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极境","text":"蒂亚戈，别离他太近，这家伙不太对劲！","id":53,"figure":["avg_npc_450_1",11]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.1","blackend":"0.25","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"烧伤的教徒","text":"伊比利亚必须毁灭！我们会杀死这个国家，这里将成为海洋的起点，浪涛将会触及云层，千万山峦都将无声崩毁——","id":55,"figure":["avg_npc_453_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"烧伤的教徒","text":"我们——即将——融为一体！","id":56,"figure":["avg_npc_453_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_450_1#7$1","id":57},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极境","text":"——！小心！蒂亚戈！","id":58,"figure":["avg_npc_450_1",6]},{"type":"dialog","id":59},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","blackstart2":"0.1","blackend2":"0.25","id":60},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.5","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":61},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":62},{"type":"playsound","key":"$p_imp_sword_n","volume":"0.9","id":63},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":64},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"-20","fadetime":"0.3","block":"false","id":65},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"-100","fadetime":"0.2","block":"false","id":66},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":67},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":68},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","blackstart2":"0.1","blackend2":"0.25","focus":"1","id":69},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":70},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"呃？！咳——！","id":71,"figure":["avg_npc_451_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_450_1#12$1","id":72},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极境","text":"蒂亚戈！啧，他已经开始变成怪物了！就和盐风城的记录一样！","id":73,"figure":["avg_npc_450_1",11]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.1","blackend":"0.25","id":74},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_fish_howl","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"烧伤的教徒","text":"先从你开始，叛徒。","id":76,"figure":["avg_npc_453_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"烧伤的教徒","text":"为了生命得以永恒延续，伊比利亚，不值，一提！","id":77,"figure":["avg_npc_453_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":78},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"不值一提？","id":80},{"type":"dialog","id":81},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":82},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":83},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":84},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"你在呼唤我的姓名吗？异教徒？","id":85,"figure":["avg_npc_447_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.1","blackend":"0.25","id":86},{"type":"dialogue","name":"烧伤的教徒","text":"......大审判官，你来得正好。","id":87,"figure":["avg_npc_453_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"烧伤的教徒","text":"向你们的神祈祷吧，而我们会证明，你们的神不值一提。你会见证伊比利亚沉入深渊。","id":88,"figure":["avg_npc_453_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"那不可能。","id":90,"figure":["avg_npc_447_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.1","blackend":"0.25","id":91},{"type":"dialogue","name":"烧伤的教徒","text":"......什么？","id":92,"figure":["avg_npc_453_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"我的名字是，卡门·伊·伊比利亚，九名圣徒早在给自己套上这个虚伪的称呼时，就摒弃了名字——也一并，摒弃了信仰。","id":94,"figure":["avg_npc_447_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"谎言燃烧着我们，我们一清二楚。伊比利亚从未被神明拯救，我们必须成为我们自己的神。","id":95,"figure":["avg_npc_447_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"我代表审判庭，在此宣读对你的判决，异教徒。","id":97,"figure":["avg_npc_447_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.1","blackend":"0.25","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"烧伤的教徒","text":"——","id":99,"figure":["avg_npc_453_1",0]},{"type":"text","text":"为什么会感到沉重？","id":100},{"type":"text","text":"我的身体已经被同胞接纳，我的生命已经得到升华。","id":101},{"type":"text","text":"那为什么？为什么我没法从他的提灯上挪开眼？","id":102},{"type":"text","text":"警惕？对，审判官都很强大，我在警惕。","id":103},{"type":"dialogue","name":"烧伤的教徒","text":"你可以杀死我，但是你无法杀死族群。杀死族群，海洋就会死去，陆地就会死去。","id":104,"figure":["avg_npc_453_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"烧伤的教徒","text":"你们终将在进化的浪潮中迷失自我，你们看不见这片大地的未来！这个时代臃肿、无序，我们都是被困在笼中的牲畜！","id":105,"figure":["avg_npc_453_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"烧伤的教徒","text":"我会将你和你的审判庭——","id":106,"figure":["avg_npc_453_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":107},{"type":"character","id":108},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.5","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":109},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":110},{"type":"playsound","key":"$e_skill_skulsrsword","volume":"0.9","id":111},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":112},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":113},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.1","blackend":"0.25","id":114},{"type":"dialogue","name":"烧伤的教徒","text":"......怎......","id":115,"figure":["avg_npc_453_1",0]},{"type":"text","text":"他不可思议地看着自己的身体，一段漂亮的横截面。","id":116},{"type":"text","text":"自他们开始了对格兰法洛的侵袭之后，这位坐镇礼拜堂的老审判官从未真正出手一次。","id":117},{"type":"text","text":"他没有用过他的剑，从不去碰他的手炮。他只会用提灯和法术，符合他年迈的印象。","id":118},{"type":"text","text":"是，年迈。他很老了。是一段寻常生命无法承受的岁月。","id":119},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.1","blackend":"0.25","id":120},{"type":"dialogue","name":"烧伤的教徒","text":"陆上......牲畜......你怎么可能？","id":121,"figure":["avg_npc_453_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"烧伤的教徒","text":"你......我至少可以......拖延......","id":122,"figure":["avg_npc_453_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","id":123},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"你做不到。","id":124,"figure":["avg_npc_447_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","id":125},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"崭新的生命，却连一个老迈的伊比利亚人都杀不死。这又有什么好得意的呢？","id":126,"figure":["avg_npc_447_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","id":127},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"看着我，异教徒。","id":128,"figure":["avg_npc_447_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.1","blackend":"0.25","id":129},{"type":"dialogue","name":"烧伤的教徒","text":"你......咳咳......你！","id":130,"figure":["avg_npc_453_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#6$1","id":131},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"你本为人类，却狭隘地误判了自己种族的可能性。","id":132,"figure":["avg_npc_447_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#6$1","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"我们赢下这场战争，如同千万年来，生命更迭，物竞天择。","id":134,"figure":["avg_npc_447_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#6$1","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"你，和你可悲的想法，会被伊比利亚埋葬。在你咽气之前，记得将我们的咆哮传达给你的同族。","id":136,"figure":["avg_npc_447_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#2$1","id":137},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"“大海面对的是被称作文明的古老敌人，你们毫无胜算。”","id":138,"figure":["avg_npc_447_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.1","blackend":"0.25","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"烧伤的教徒","text":"你......呃......你......什么都不明白......","id":140,"figure":["avg_npc_453_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":141},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":142},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bodyfalldown1","volume":"1","id":143},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1","id":144},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":145},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":146},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"......","id":148,"figure":["avg_npc_447_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#5$1","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"他还好吗？","id":150,"figure":["avg_npc_447_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_450_1#2$1","id":151},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$dignified_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_dignified_loop.mp3","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1","delay":"0.5","id":152,"musicid":1},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极境","text":"从刚才开始就在努力抢救了——！但是，伤口太深！","id":153,"figure":["avg_npc_450_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_450_1#12$1","id":154},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极境","text":"如果凯尔希医生......得把他带到医生那里，审判官阁下！凯尔希医生在哪里？","id":155,"figure":["avg_npc_450_1",11]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","id":156},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"就在礼拜堂。","id":157,"figure":["avg_npc_447_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","id":158},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"罗德岛的成员，话我得说清楚。他的背叛行径不容辩驳，他必须受到惩罚。","id":159,"figure":["avg_npc_447_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","id":160},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"窝藏深海教徒，知而不报，不仅让审判庭错失良机，更让无数惩戒军袍泽与达里奥深陷苦境。","id":161,"figure":["avg_npc_447_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#3$1","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"......啧，老家伙。","id":163,"figure":["avg_npc_451_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#3$1","id":164},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"你有多大岁数？一百岁？你为什么......呃啊......还能装得这么朝气蓬勃？","id":165,"figure":["avg_npc_451_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#2$1","id":166},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"职责如此。","id":167,"figure":["avg_npc_447_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#3$1","id":168},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"所以你一定......咳咳......咳啊......知道很多事情......","id":169,"figure":["avg_npc_451_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#3$1","id":170},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"告诉我，审判官。你必须说实话，低劣的刽子手......","id":171,"figure":["avg_npc_451_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#3$1","id":172},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"你们......为什么......哈......要毁灭那样一群怀揣希望，重建......家园的......人们？","id":173,"figure":["avg_npc_451_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#3$1","id":174},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"你们......你们......","id":175,"figure":["avg_npc_451_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_450_1#2$1","id":176},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极境","text":"别讲话了！蒂亚戈，血止不住！","id":177,"figure":["avg_npc_450_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#3$1","id":178},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"哈......哈啊......不，我要问。","id":179,"figure":["avg_npc_451_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#3$1","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"你们，审判庭！你们从格兰法洛带走的阿戈尔人里，真的有深海教会的异教徒吗？","id":181,"figure":["avg_npc_451_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"......","id":183,"figure":["avg_npc_447_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#3$1","id":184},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"告诉我......你们是不是，出于......咳，可笑的猜忌，怀疑，就，害死了那群，好人？","id":185,"figure":["avg_npc_451_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"普通市民无权得知审判庭的机密。","id":187,"figure":["avg_npc_447_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#4$1","id":188},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"你......！","id":189,"figure":["avg_npc_451_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","id":190},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"得知真相无益于你苟延残喘的生命，蒂亚戈。","id":191,"figure":["avg_npc_447_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#3$1","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"不，不不不......求求你......求求你，我将要死去，你还不愿坦白吗......","id":193,"figure":["avg_npc_451_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#3$1","id":194},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"至少......马琳她......告诉我......","id":195,"figure":["avg_npc_451_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#2$1","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"格兰法洛的阿戈尔卷宗已被尘封，我不可能将其告诉你一介平民。","id":197,"figure":["avg_npc_447_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#3$1","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"......不......咳咳，咳啊......","id":199,"figure":["avg_npc_451_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#3$1","id":200},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"我......我诅咒你，我绝不原谅你们！","id":201,"figure":["avg_npc_451_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#3$1","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"伊比利亚......伊比......必将......","id":203,"figure":["avg_npc_451_1",2]},{"type":"dialog","id":204},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":205},{"type":"text","text":"咒骂的话语并没有说出口。","id":206},{"type":"text","text":"老蒂亚戈看着昏暗潮湿的天花板，有一滴水即将从木梁滴下。","id":207},{"type":"text","text":"滴答。","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"......","id":209},{"type":"dialog","id":210},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":211},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_450_1#2$1","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极境","text":"......","id":213,"figure":["avg_npc_450_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_450_1#2$1","id":214},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极境","text":"......他走了。","id":215,"figure":["avg_npc_450_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_450_1#9$1","id":216},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极境","text":"所以，真相是什么？","id":217,"figure":["avg_npc_450_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#7$1","id":218},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"应该和你也没关系，罗德岛的成员。","id":219,"figure":["avg_npc_447_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#7$1","id":220},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"现在回到凯尔希的身边去，我们被拖延了太久，伊比利亚之眼极有可能失守。","id":221,"figure":["avg_npc_447_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_450_1#9$1","id":222},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极境","text":"请告诉我。","id":223,"figure":["avg_npc_450_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_450_1#9$1","id":224},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极境","text":"我是罗德岛的成员，也愿意与审判庭合作，但在那之前，我是个伊比利亚人。","id":225,"figure":["avg_npc_450_1",8]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极境","text":"我和蒂亚戈相处时间不长。但我刚才意识到......他不会诅咒伊比利亚。因为伊比利亚真的被他视作家园。","id":226,"figure":["avg_npc_450_1",8]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极境","text":"意识到之后，我就更不能......","id":227,"figure":["avg_npc_450_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_450_1#11$1","id":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极境","text":"卡门阁下，在看见家乡的诸多悲剧之后，您总不能......就叫我这么轻描淡写地无视。","id":229,"figure":["avg_npc_450_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#2$1","id":230},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"......","id":231,"figure":["avg_npc_447_1",1]},{"type":"text","text":"卡门扫视了一眼躺在极境怀里的老工人。他的眼神里流露出些微不同的情感。","id":232},{"type":"text","text":"沉默片刻后，他开口了。","id":233},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#7$1","id":234},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"从格兰法洛带走的一百三十余名阿戈尔人中，有半数与深海教会牵连。就连过去镇守在此的惩戒军中，都揪出了不少叛徒。","id":235,"figure":["avg_npc_447_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#7$1","id":236},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"他们窃取了大量关于伊比利亚远航时代的资料，阻碍审判庭，并始终在谋划将格兰法洛化为大海侵袭陆地的入口。","id":237,"figure":["avg_npc_447_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#7$1","id":238},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"为首的是一名女性主教，阿戈尔岛民，她被人们称作“马琳”。","id":239,"figure":["avg_npc_447_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#2$1","id":240},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"现在，埋葬他吧。","id":241,"figure":["avg_npc_447_1",1]},{"type":"dialog","id":242},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":243},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":244},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":245},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d8/Avg_bg_27_g22_goldenboat_hall.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":246},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":247},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$exciting_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_exciting02_loop.mp3","fadetime":"3","volume":"0.8","id":248,"musicid":2},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_456_1#1$1","id":249},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"强壮，你们合力，足以引领族群。","id":250,"figure":["avg_npc_456_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_456_1#1$1","id":251},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"可是，你们并不如此打算，我感到疑惑。","id":252,"figure":["avg_npc_456_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_456_1#1$1","id":253},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"族群，究竟被你们如何对待？","id":254,"figure":["avg_npc_456_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_456_1#1$1","id":255},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"意志，诞生所有。我们可以，跨过鸿沟。","id":256,"figure":["avg_npc_456_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_456_1#1$1","id":257},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"环境，完整纯洁。杂质，不被需要。","id":258,"figure":["avg_npc_456_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_456_1#1$1","id":259},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"亲代，试图寻找答案，我还不清楚问题，我还无法询问。","id":260,"figure":["avg_npc_456_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":261},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_446_1#1$1","id":262},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.5","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":263},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":264},{"type":"playsound","key":"$e_skill_skulsrsword","volume":"0.9","id":265},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_attack_heavy","id":266},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_sp_ballista","volume":"0.4","id":267},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":268},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":269},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","id":270},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"-200","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":271},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_456_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":272},{"type":"jump","name":"middle","xpos":"300","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":273},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":274},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"（骨骼摩擦的声音）","id":275,"figure":["avg_npc_456_1",0]},{"type":"character","id":276},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_446_1#9$1","id":277},{"type":"dialogue","name":"船长阿方索","text":"海洋的婴儿，都这么快学会说话吗？","id":278,"figure":["avg_npc_446_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#7$1","id":279},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"怎么，船长先生？难道您的孤独已经让您对会说话的海嗣感到亲切了吗？","id":280,"figure":["avg_1023_ghost2_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#7$1","id":281},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"到现在为止，它身上每一道可见的伤口，都是我留下的。","id":282,"figure":["avg_1023_ghost2_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_446_1#1$1","id":283},{"type":"dialogue","name":"船长阿方索","text":"啐。","id":284,"figure":["avg_npc_446_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_446_1#7$1","id":285},{"type":"dialogue","name":"船长阿方索","text":"它还活蹦乱跳，好戏才刚刚开始。","id":286,"figure":["avg_npc_446_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_456_1#1$1","id":287},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"......战斗，缺乏意义。","id":288,"figure":["avg_npc_456_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_456_1#1$1","id":289},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"离开，正确的选择。","id":290,"figure":["avg_npc_456_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":291},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.5","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":292},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":293},{"type":"playsound","key":"$e_skill_skulsrsword","volume":"0.4","id":294},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_attack_heavy","volume":"0.9","id":295},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_bone_rub","volume":"0.9","id":296},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":297},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_rockfall","volume":"1","id":298},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":299},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.9","id":300},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1","id":301},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":302},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_446_1#3$1","id":303},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":304},{"type":"dialogue","name":"船长阿方索","text":"唔，站住！","id":305,"figure":["avg_npc_446_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#5$1","id":306},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"它切开墙壁离开了，伊比利亚人何必要把这艘船造得这么复杂呢？","id":307,"figure":["avg_1023_ghost2_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_446_1#3$1","id":308},{"type":"dialogue","name":"船长阿方索","text":"我不允许它继续这样作践我的船，加西亚！","id":309,"figure":["avg_npc_446_1",2]},{"type":"dialog","id":310},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":311},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.9","id":312},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_452_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":313},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":314},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","id":315},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"带着这可犯规了哦。","id":316,"figure":["avg_1023_ghost2_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_446_1#1$1","id":317},{"type":"dialogue","name":"船长阿方索","text":"你以为这么多年，我们是如何在怪物们的包围下，还能保证这艘船不至于千疮百孔然后沉没的？只靠布雷奥甘的技术吗？","id":318,"figure":["avg_npc_446_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_446_1#1$1","id":319},{"type":"dialogue","name":"船长阿方索","text":"我们把那些有威胁的、足够有破坏性的生物，统统杀死。然后，再由幸存者一点一点缝补它们留下的创痕。","id":320,"figure":["avg_npc_446_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_446_1#1$1","id":321},{"type":"dialogue","name":"船长阿方索","text":"这一只，算是其中聪明的，但绝不是最强大的。","id":322,"figure":["avg_npc_446_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_446_1#7$1","id":323},{"type":"dialogue","name":"船长阿方索","text":"我现在没心情和你玩游戏，玩笑到此为止。在它干出什么不可挽回的事情之前，猎杀它。","id":324,"figure":["avg_npc_446_1",6]},{"type":"dialog","id":325},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":326},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":327},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":328},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5d/Avg_bg_27_g23_goldenboat_pass.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":329},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":330},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_nervous_loop.mp3","fadetime":"3","volume":"0.8","id":331,"musicid":3},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":332},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_rockfall","volume":"1","id":333},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":334},{"type":"text","text":"逃走的海嗣轻而易举地切开了墙壁。它能闻见，闻见这个奇异的方盒外，就是同胞与水。","id":335},{"type":"text","text":"它受伤了，它需要愈合，它需要养分，它需要更多时间。那个无鳞同胞为它争取了喘息之机，但时间并不充裕。","id":336},{"type":"text","text":"还有很多事情没有准备好。","id":337},{"type":"dialog","id":338},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#2$1","fadetime":"1","id":339},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":340},{"type":"dialogue","name":"审判官艾丽妮","text":"......？！海嗣！","id":341,"figure":["avg_4009_irene_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_456_1#1$1","id":342},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"......","id":343,"figure":["avg_npc_456_1",0]},{"type":"text","text":"海嗣没有言语。","id":344},{"type":"text","text":"因为对方不是同胞。不是会说话的同胞。不是无鳞的同胞。","id":345},{"type":"text","text":"那么眼前的这个试图反抗的弱小生物，就只是寻常的生命。处于循环之中的生命。","id":346},{"type":"text","text":"应当捕食。","id":347},{"type":"text","text":"做出了这样的判断后，海嗣几乎在瞬间向艾丽妮伸出了尖牙利爪。","id":348},{"type":"dialog","id":349},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_456_1#1$1","id":350},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.5","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":351},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":352},{"type":"playsound","key":"$e_skill_skulsrsword","volume":"0.4","id":353},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_attack_heavy","volume":"0.9","id":354},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_bone_rub","volume":"0.9","id":355},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":356},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":357},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#4$1","id":358},{"type":"dialogue","name":"审判官艾丽妮","text":"（好快——它的身体和先前不一样了！？）","id":359,"figure":["avg_4009_irene_1",3]},{"type":"dialog","id":360},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.5","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":361},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":362},{"type":"playsound","key":"$swordtsing2","volume":"1","id":363},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.2","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":364},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.5","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":365},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":366},{"type":"playsound","key":"$swordtsing1","volume":"0.9","id":367},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":368},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":369},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_456_1#1$1","id":370},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"......","id":371,"figure":["avg_npc_456_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#4$1","id":372},{"type":"dialogue","name":"审判官艾丽妮","text":"好硬？！","id":373,"figure":["avg_4009_irene_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"审判官艾丽妮","text":"（糟糕——这下躲不开——）","id":374,"figure":["avg_4009_irene_1",3]},{"type":"dialog","id":375},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":376},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","id":377},{"type":"move","name":"middle","ypos":"300","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":378},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_452_1#1$1","fadetime":"0.3","id":379},{"type":"move","name":"middle","ypos":"-300","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":380},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":381},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bodyfalldown1","volume":"1","id":382},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_attack_heavy","volume":"0.9","id":383},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_bone_rub","volume":"0.9","id":384},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":385},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":386},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_456_1#1$1","id":387},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"......！","id":388,"figure":["avg_npc_456_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_452_1#1$1","id":389},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":390},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大副","text":"（嘶吼）","id":391,"figure":["avg_npc_452_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_452_1#1$1","id":392},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大副","text":"（不自然地发声）......站......起来......逃。","id":393,"figure":["avg_npc_452_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#2$1","id":394},{"type":"dialogue","name":"审判官艾丽妮","text":"——你？！你会说话？伊比利亚语？","id":395,"figure":["avg_4009_irene_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_452_1#1$1","id":396},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大副","text":"（不自然地发声）......我......救你。别让......他知道。","id":397,"figure":["avg_npc_452_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_452_1#1$1","id":398},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大副","text":"（不自然地发声）别让......阿方索......知道......我还是......人类。","id":399,"figure":["avg_npc_452_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_456_1#1$1","id":400},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"语言，你也懂得。","id":401,"figure":["avg_npc_456_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_456_1#1$1","id":402},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"效率，略显低下。信息不够，时间太短，如有必要，我会完整。","id":403,"figure":["avg_npc_456_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_456_1#1$1","id":404},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"族群，你们自成一派。与子代，相互捕食。","id":405,"figure":["avg_npc_456_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_456_1#1$1","id":406},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"你们，有所缺失。","id":407,"figure":["avg_npc_456_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_452_1#1$1","id":408},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大副","text":"（不自然地发声）阿方索......赶来......不快。","id":409,"figure":["avg_npc_452_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_452_1#1$1","id":410},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大副","text":"（不自然地发声）你......逃。","id":411,"figure":["avg_npc_452_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_456_1#1$1","id":412},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"族群，无需豢养。","id":413,"figure":["avg_npc_456_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_456_1#1$1","id":414},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"血肉，应自觉奉献。","id":415,"figure":["avg_npc_456_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_452_1#1$1","id":416},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大副","text":"（哀嚎）——！","id":417,"figure":["avg_npc_452_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":418},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_456_1#1$1","id":419},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.5","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":420},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":421},{"type":"playsound","key":"$e_skill_skulsrsword","volume":"0.4","id":422},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_attack_heavy","volume":"0.9","id":423},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_bone_rub","volume":"0.9","id":424},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":425},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":426},{"type":"character","id":427},{"type":"playsound","key":"$blooddrop","volume":"0.9","id":428},{"type":"text","text":"口吐人言的大副被海嗣的尖牙洞穿。","id":429},{"type":"text","text":"并非轻敌，也并非被艾丽妮分散了注意力。而是海嗣的动作，明显有了变化。","id":430},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_452_1#1$1","id":431},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大副","text":"......你......","id":432,"figure":["avg_npc_452_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_452_1#1$1","id":433},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大副","text":"阿方索......快......快......","id":434,"figure":["avg_npc_452_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":435},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","id":436},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.5","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":437},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":438},{"type":"playsound","key":"$swordtsing1","volume":"0.9","id":439},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":440},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":441},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#4$1","id":442},{"type":"dialogue","name":"审判官艾丽妮","text":"（连它的外壳都刺不破！）","id":443,"figure":["avg_4009_irene_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#4$1","id":444},{"type":"dialogue","name":"审判官艾丽妮","text":"（再这样下去......我......）","id":445,"figure":["avg_4009_irene_1",3]},{"type":"dialog","id":446},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":447},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":448},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":449},{"type":"text","text":"艾丽妮。你知道这里是哪里。","id":450},{"type":"text","text":"是！是审判庭的......","id":451},{"type":"text","text":"地下。每一位大审判官都曾在这里目睹真相。","id":452},{"type":"text","text":"真相......","id":453},{"type":"text","text":"思考一件事，艾丽妮。审判庭为何而战？","id":454},{"type":"text","text":"为伊比利亚的洁净与德行，为律法与经文的圣洁而战。","id":455},{"type":"text","text":"那倘若被世人奉为真理的观念只是肤浅的表象，律法无法触及，经文不曾预言，万物的道德都不适用，你该如何判断？","id":456},{"type":"text","text":"我......会以自己的标准来判断。","id":457},{"type":"text","text":"即使抛弃一直以来你所秉承的正邪之分？","id":458},{"type":"text","text":"是的！","id":459},{"type":"text","text":"说起来总是容易的，艾丽妮。言传身教都没有意义，我不会同你赘述。","id":460},{"type":"text","text":"长官......","id":461},{"type":"text","text":"但是。","id":462},{"type":"dialog","id":463},{"type":"background","id":464},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":465},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":466},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_183#3","fadetime":"1","id":467},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":468},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大审判官达里奥","text":"终有一日，你所面临的敌人会逼迫你抛弃你所建立起的一切。信仰，道德，伦理，都会被蹂躏亵渎，变得毫无意义。","id":469,"figure":["avg_npc_183",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_183#3","id":470},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大审判官达里奥","text":"而后，如果你还能重建起内心的信仰，无论那是什么，都将支撑你打败敌人。","id":471,"figure":["avg_npc_183",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大审判官达里奥","text":"在看清真相，体会更加残酷的历史前，所作所为，都是纸上谈兵。","id":472,"figure":["avg_npc_183",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大审判官达里奥","text":"我不会对你的未来指点什么。在那一刻来临时，我只要你记住，艾丽妮。","id":473,"figure":["avg_npc_183",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大审判官达里奥","text":"你必须是伊比利亚最后的防线。","id":474,"figure":["avg_npc_183",2]},{"type":"dialog","id":475},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":476},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":477},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5d/Avg_bg_27_g23_goldenboat_pass.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":478},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":479},{"type":"dialog","id":480},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","afrom":"0","rfrom":"0","gfrom":"0","bfrom":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":481},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_gunsingle","volume":"0.9","id":482},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_sp_ballista","volume":"0.4","id":483},{"type":"playsound","key":"$tactfulboost","volume":"0.3","id":484},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"false","id":485},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":486},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":487},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$batmeeting_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_batmeeting_loop.mp3","fadetime":"3","volume":"0.8","id":488,"musicid":4},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_456_1#1$1","id":489},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"不......","id":490,"figure":["avg_npc_456_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_456_1#1$1","id":491},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"生存，并非你的目的。你却能，有所突破。","id":492,"figure":["avg_npc_456_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":493},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","id":494},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","afrom":"0","rfrom":"0","gfrom":"0","bfrom":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":495},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_gunsingle","volume":"0.9","id":496},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_sp_ballista","volume":"0.4","id":497},{"type":"playsound","key":"$tactfulboost","volume":"0.3","id":498},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"false","id":499},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":500},{"type":"dialog","id":501},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":502},{"type":"image","xScale":"0.9","yScale":"0.9","x":"80","y":"-40","id":503},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleTo":"0.8","yScaleTo":"0.8","duration":"70","xTo":"0","yTo":"0","block":"false","id":504},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":505},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":506},{"type":"text","text":"艾丽妮举起了手炮。","id":507},{"type":"text","text":"海嗣坚不可摧的身体上赫然出现了第二个空洞，巨大的热流融化了坚固异常的墙壁。","id":508},{"type":"text","text":"喷薄的高温让周遭仿若火海。大副呜咽着退到一旁，怔怔看着眼前的景象。","id":509},{"type":"text","text":"海嗣从未被如此的法术包围过，它感到无所适从，尽管它迅速适应。","id":510},{"type":"text","text":"但审判官的炮火，不会在提灯熄灭前停止。","id":511},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"放开它，怪物。闻一闻源石的味道。","id":512},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"你没有犯下任何过错，神圣的经文也并未提及你们的存在。","id":513},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"现在，只是我作为一个伊比利亚人，对你下达判决。","id":514},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"海洋的灾厄必须被消灭，你无权生存。","id":515},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"以伊比利亚之名。","id":516},{"type":"dialog","id":517},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":518},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":519},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":520},{"type":"image","id":521},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":522},{"type":"dialog","id":523},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":524},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":525}],"characters":["蒂亚戈","极境","烧伤的教徒","？？？","圣徒卡门","海嗣","船长阿方索","幽灵鲨","审判官艾丽妮","大副","大审判官达里奥","艾丽妮"]}